.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.IX Header "DESCRIPTION"
This is a collection of functions for dealing with \s-1PPI\s0 objects, many of
which originated in Perl::Critic.  They are organized into
modules by the kind of \s-1PPI\s0 class they relate to, by replacing the \*(L"\s-1PPI\*(R"\s0 at the
front of the module name with \*(L"PPIx::Utilities\*(R", e.g. functionality related to
PPI::Nodes is in PPIx::Utilities::Node.
